'''葛利斯832c'''（'''Gliese 832 c''' 或 '''Gl 832 c'''、'''GJ 832 c'''），是一顆距離地球約16光年，位於[[天鶴座|天鶴座]]的[[太陽系外行星|太陽系外行星]]，母恆星是[[紅矮星|紅矮星]][[葛利斯832|葛利斯832]]<ref name = "space.com"/>。該行星的[[地球相似指數|地球相似指數]]為0.81，是已知系外行星中該指數最高的行星之一<ref name = "phl">{{Citation|author = Abel Mendez Torres|url = http://phl.upr.edu/press-releases/gliese832|title = A Nearby Super-Earth with the Right Temperature but Extreme Seasons|date = June 25, 2014|accessdate = 2014-07-01|archive-date = 2019-05-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190513221647/http://phl.upr.edu/press-releases/gliese832|dead-url = no}}</ref>。它位於母恆星的[[適居帶|適居帶]]內。

葛利斯832c被發現是至今为止潛在適居系外行星中距離地球最近的幾個候选者之一<ref name = "space.com"/>。

==概要==
葛利斯832c的質量大約是[[地球|地球]]的5.4倍。它的預期表面溫度類似地球，但是會隨著環繞恆星時與母恆星距離變動而改變。葛利斯832c的[[軌道離心率|軌道離心率]]相對地球而言較高，軌道週期約36日<ref name = "phl"/>。葛利斯832c表面的[[行星平衡溫度|平均平衡溫度]]推測是253 [[熱力學溫標|K]]（−20℃）<ref name = "phl"/>。但是它可能擁有濃密大氣層，使它的表面溫度可能遠高於平衡溫度，並且更類似[[金星|金星]]<ref>{{Citation|author = Nancy Atkinson|url = http://www.universetoday.com/112806/nearby-super-earth-is-best-habitable-candidate-so-far-astronomers-say/|title = Nearby Super-Earth is Best Habitable Candidate So Far, Astronomers Say|date = June 25, 2014|accessdate = June 26, 2014|archive-date = 2019-06-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190608115134/https://www.universetoday.com/112806/nearby-super-earth-is-best-habitable-candidate-so-far-astronomers-say/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name = "dailystar">{{Citation|author = David Snelling|url = http://www.dailystar.co.uk/tech/385831/Gliese-832c-alien-planet-is-discovered-by-astronomers|title = Alien planet discovered! And it's not that far away|date = June 26, 2014|accessdate = 2014-07-01|archive-date = 2014-11-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141101082700/http://www.dailystar.co.uk/tech/385831/Gliese-832c-alien-planet-is-discovered-by-astronomers|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

葛利斯832c是位於所屬母恆星適居帶內的[[超級地球|超級地球]]。雖然它和母恆星的距離遠低於日地距離，但其母恆星是紅矮星，因此其所接收的能量相當於地球接收的太陽輻射能<ref name = "space.com">{{Citation|author = Mike Wall|publisher = [[space.com|space.com]]|url = http://www.space.com/26357-exoplanet-habitable-zone-gliese-832c.html|title = Nearby Alien Planet May Be Capable of Supporting Life|date = June 25, 2014|accessdate = June 26, 2014|archive-date = 2018-07-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180712234753/https://www.space.com/26357-exoplanet-habitable-zone-gliese-832c.html|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

==發現與意义==
葛利斯832c是由[[新南威尔士大学|新南威尔士大学]]的天文學家{{link-en|羅伯特·威滕邁耶|Robert A. Wittenmyer}}（Robert A. Wittenmyer）領導的國際團隊發現<ref name = "phl"/><ref name = "space.com"/>。該行星被發現時是「[[潛在適居太陽系外行星列表|適居太陽系外行星目錄]]」內的行星中距離地球第2近的<ref name = "phl"/>。

葛利斯832c的發現者描述該行星是「至今最近且最好的適居行星候選者」<ref>{{Citation|author = Hannah Osborne|publisher = ''[[国际财经时报|International Business Times]]''|url = http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/gliese-832c-alien-most-earth-like-planet-found-16-light-years-away-1454270|title = Gliese 832 c: 'Best Habitable World Candidate' Discovered 16 Light Years Away|date = June 25, 2014|accessdate = June 16, 2014|archive-date = 2019-07-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190713131252/https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/gliese-832c-alien-most-earth-like-planet-found-16-light-years-away-1454270|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

天文學家將對葛利斯832c進行更進一步研究以確認它是否適合生命存在<ref name = "dailystar"/>。

